Params-Validate-Aggregated

B<Params::Validate::Aggregated> separates out parameters for several
functions from a single list of parameters.  The functions are all
assumed to use B<Params::Validate> to validate their inputs, and to
only use I<named> parameters.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


